                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8695" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0255</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2249 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">以G为纲：百果园的公司治理实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">G as a Outline:  The Corporate Governance Practices of Pagoda</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑耀洲，郑丽娟，何春艳，刘莹，崔淼，李树文，江诗松</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中南财经政法大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳百果园实业（集团）股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">百果园；ESG；公司治理；ESG治理；全面风险管理；2024百优案例；重点项目；系列4-2</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Pagoda, ESG, Corporate Governance, ESG Governance, Comprehensive Risk Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业可持续发展与中国式现代化的五位一体总体布局是高度相关的，是中国企业为高质量发展做出贡献的必由之路。目前，随着可持续发展理念的不断深化，ESG（环境、社会和治理）发展已成大势。同时，居民消费意识逐渐转变，水果需求持续上升，企业抓住机遇来优化公司治理、以适应时代发展是提升竞争优势、实现高质量发展的关键之一。百果园作为“中国水果零售连锁第一股”，在“水果生意并不好做”的业界共识以及ESG需求下的公司治理方面交出了满分的答卷。它始终强调公司治理对其他治理领域的引领作用，并强调ESG理念与公司治理理念相融合，以实现可持续发展。本案例以ESG为背景、百果园的公司治理实践为主线，从决策、激励、监督的公司治理机制以及防线构建、风险识别、处理、回应的全面风险管理这两个维度展开，详细描述了百果园将ESG理念与公司治理实践深度融合的全过程。该案例旨在深化学生对ESG中G（治理）相关知识的理解，提高学生识别、分析和解决公司治理问题的能力，增强学生的风险防控意识，进而推动企业的可持续发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> Corporate sustainability is highly relevant to the five-in-one overall layout of Chinese-style modernization, and is a must for Chinese companies to contribute to high-quality development. At present, with the deepening of the concept of sustainable development, ESG (environmental, social and governance) development has become a major trend. At the same time, residents&#39; consumption awareness is gradually changing, and the demand for fruits continues to rise. Seizing the opportunity to optimize corporate governance to adapt to the development of the times is one of the keys to enhance competitive advantage and achieve high-quality development. As the “No. 1 Fruit Retail Chain Stock in China”, Pagoda has delivered a perfect answer to the industry consensus that “the fruit business is not doing well” and the corporate governance under ESG requirements. It has always emphasized the leading role of corporate governance for other areas of governance and the integration of ESG concepts with corporate governance concepts to achieve sustainable development.The case takes ESG as the background and the corporate governance practice of Pagoda as the main line, and describes in detail the whole process of Pagoda&#39;s in-depth integration of ESG concepts and corporate governance practice from the two dimensions of the corporate governance mechanism of decision-making, incentives, and supervision, as well as the comprehensive risk management of the construction of the line of defense, and the risk identification, treatment, and response. The case aims to deepen students&#39; understanding of G (governance) related knowledge in ESG, improve students&#39; ability to identify, analyze and solve corporate governance problems, enhance students&#39; awareness of risk prevention and control, and then promote the sustainable development of enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业伦理与社会责任》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公司治理的概念、公司治理的驱动因素、公司治理机制、全面风险管理机制</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-10</td>
                            </tr>
